title: GTA 6 Hacker "Teapot" Has Been Arrested in the UK

media:group.media:title: GTA 6 Hacker "Teapot" Has Been Arrested in the UK
media:group.media:description:
The teenage hacker most recently known as teapot (also goes under other aliases like white, and SigmA) was arrested in Oxford shire UK on suspicion of hacking and is currently held in police custody.
